{
  "texts": [
    "These data were scored with guidelines that were different from the adapted or standard interview manuals.",
    "So, these data were included for exploratory analyses, without the expectation that our model would perform well on them.",
    "Because they were scored differently from all the other datasets, they were never included in the training sets.",
    "Each of these datasets is described in more detail below.",
    "Dataset 1: Autobiographical memories (King et al., 2022) King et al. (2022) examined how retrieving memories from an observer perspective (as opposed to a first-person perspective) changed the narratives."
  ]
}